        Parameters:
        f - an arraylist of TwowayTicketPlan
        dtoFrom - Departure flight departure time window start hour

        atoFrom - Departure flight arrival time window start hour
        atoTo - Departure flight arrival time window end hour

        abackTo - Return flight arrival time window end hour
